---
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import '../styles/global.css';

---
<section class="fade-in-up">
  <div class="banner d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center container-fluid position-relative" style="min-height: 80vh; color: #2c3e50;">
    <!-- Simple animated background -->
    <div class="position-absolute top-0 start-0 w-100 h-100 overflow-hidden" style="z-index: 1;">
      <div class="floating-elements">
        <div class="floating-element element-1"></div>
        <div class="floating-element element-2"></div>
        <div class="floating-element element-3"></div>
        <div class="floating-element element-4"></div>
        <div class="floating-element element-5"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Gradient overlay -->
    <div class="position-absolute top-0 start-0 w-100 h-100" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(236, 240, 241, 0.9), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9), rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.9)); z-index: 2;"></div>
    
    <!-- Animated background elements -->
    <div class="code-background" style="z-index: 3;">
      <div class="code-line">{'{'}</div>
      <div class="code-line">{'  '}<span class="code-keyword">"nombre"</span>: <span class="code-string">"TekohaTech"</span>,</div>
      <div class="code-line">{'  '}<span class="code-keyword">"especialidad"</span>: <span class="code-string">"Soluciones Web"</span>,</div>
      <div class="code-line">{'  '}<span class="code-keyword">"misión"</span>: <span class="code-string">"Innovar en digital"</span></div>
      <div class="code-line">{'}'}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-12 text-center banner-content" style="z-index: 4;">
      <h1 class="gradient-text mt-4 mb-4 section-title">TekohaTech</h1>
      <p class="h5 text-dark mt-2 mx-auto px-3 px-md-5" style="max-width: 900px; color: #2c3e50 !important;">
        "Bienvenido! Tekoha significa 'pueblo' o 'comunidad' en guaraní, reflejando nuestro compromiso de ofrecerte servicios de diseño y desarrollo web que te ayuden a destacar en línea. Lleva tu presencia en la web al siguiente nivel con nosotros."
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4">
        <a href="#contacto" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Comienza tu proyecto</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
  h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 576px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
  .code-background {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    opacity: 0.1;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    color: #ffffff;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .code-line {
    margin: 2px 0;
    animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .code-line:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .code-line:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
  .code-line:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
  .code-line:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }

  .code-keyword {
    color: #e74c3c;
  }

  .code-string {
    color: #3498db;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
  }

  /* Lightweight floating elements */
  .floating-elements {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .floating-element {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #3498db, #1abc9c);
    opacity: 0.2;
    animation: floatAnimation 8s infinite ease-in-out;
  }

  .element-1 {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    top: 20%;
    left: 10%;
    animation-delay: 0s;
  }

  .element-2 {
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    top: 60%;
    left: 80%;
    animation-delay: 1s;
  }

  .element-3 {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    top: 40%;
    left: 50%;
    animation-delay: 2s;
  }

  .element-4 {
    width: 25px;
    height: 25px;
    top: 70%;
    left: 20%;
    animation-delay: 3s;
  }

  .element-5 {
    width: 35px;
    height: 35px;
    top: 30%;
    left: 70%;
    animation-delay: 4s;
  }

  @keyframes floatAnimation {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg);
    }
    25% {
      transform: translate(20px, 20px) rotate(90deg);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translate(0, 40px) rotate(180deg);
    }
    75% {
      transform: translate(-20px, 20px) rotate(270deg);
    }
  }

  .banner-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 3;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background-color: #1abc9c;
    border-color: #1abc9c;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 12px 30px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background-color: #16a085;
    border-color: #16a085;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(26, 188, 156, 0.3);
  }
</style>